(19, 'faq', 'How will I know how much referral commission I make every month?', '<p>&nbsp;You will be able to check your income report in your member&rsquo;s area.</p>', NULL, '', '2011-07-25', NULL, NULL, 'truth-junction-content.php', '', ''),
(20, 'faq', 'How do I know if one of my people that I have invited has registered to be a member?', '<p>&nbsp;You will receive an email notifying you that someone has registered and you will be given their name and email address.<br />\r\nNb; a new member has to add the name of the person who invited them!<br />\r\nIf you do not have a referrer that is if you found us via the internet, use Truth Junction and 000000 as referrer name and id respectively. <br />\r\n(Please be honest to the person who invited you OK)</p>', NULL, '', '2011-04-05', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', ''),
(21, 'faq', 'When people cancel their Membership, how does that affect my commission?', '<p>You will lose only that persons commission. <br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '', '2011-04-05', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', ''),
(22, 'faq', 'Can I invite anyone around the world to become a member of TRUTH JUNCTION?', '<p>&nbsp;No, but we will be going international very soon. That is when our System will be available to the entire international community.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '', '2011-04-05', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', ''),
(23, 'faq', 'How am I paid my commission?', '<p>your commission will be paid into the bank account you designated. <br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '', '2011-04-05', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', ''),
(24, 'faq', 'What if I do not have money to start?', '<p>&nbsp;If you do not even have P220 to start, we suggest that you cut down on fast food, cigarettes, cell phone calls or anything else that is not absolutely essential. You desperately need this opportunity, so make a plan. <br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '', '2011-07-25', NULL, NULL, 'truth-junction-content.php', '', ''),
(25, 'faq', 'What do I have to loose?', '<p>Absolutely nothing. With only P220 a month you get all the business consultancy services for the whole month.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '', '2011-07-25', NULL, NULL, 'truth-junction-content.php', '', ''),
(26, 'faq', 'Do I still pay my subscriptions once I am making a profit?', '<p>&nbsp;No. As soon as your commission is higher than your subscription we will not debit your account. Your subscription will be deducted from your commission.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '', '2011-04-05', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', ''),
(27, 'faq', 'How do I know your System is legal?', '<p>We provide legal services that add huge value to our members.<br />\r\nCompany Registration&nbsp;Number; CO2010/10462</p>', NULL, '', '2011-08-20', NULL, NULL, 'truth-junction-content.php', '', ''),
(28, 'faq', 'I am a tertiary student and I hold a student account, can I use it to make my subscriptions?', '<p>Yes, but you can open a separate bank account (it is so so cheap!) and use it to pay your subscriptions. I also encourage everyone to open a separate bank account so they can easily monitor their commissions.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '', '2011-04-05', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', ''),
(29, 'faq', 'My child is less than 18 years, can I make him a member?', '<p>No!!! <br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '', '2011-04-05', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', ''),
(30, 'faq', 'How safe is my banking details and financial security after making an online transaction?', '<p>&nbsp;We are a member of&nbsp;<span class="red"><a href="http://www.vcs.co.za/"><strong><font size="2">virtual card services</font></strong></a></span><font size="2">&nbsp;</font> (V.C.S) authorizers of online payment. Recognized by all banks worldwide. So all payments are done via V.C.S just like buying goods at a supermarket using your credit or debit card. <br />\r\n(research more about V.C.S or visit <a href="http://www.vcs.co.za">www.vcs.co.za</a>)<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '', '2011-08-20', NULL, NULL, 'truth-junction-content.php', '', ''),
(32, '', 'Policies', '<p><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0); "><strong>Privacy Policy</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0); "><br />\r\nAt Truth Junction PTY Ltd, we respect your privacy and your personal information. For this reason, we have prepared this privacy policy to let you know how we will treat any personal information that we may have about you. We will take all reasonable measures, in accordance with this privacy policy, to protect your personal information and to keep it confidential.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>What is Personal Information?</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nAny information which you provide to us, whether on any forms you complete or through the use of any of our services or facilities, will be regarded by us as personal information.<br />\r\nAny information about what you buy, where you shop, where you bank, and all related information will also be regarded as personal information.<br />\r\nIn short, any information that we know about you will be regarded as your personal information.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>How we collect your Personal Information</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nIn order to make your use of our Internet Services as successful and pleasurable as possible, it is necessary for us to find out exactly what you need and want from us. One of the ways we can do this is by collecting and analyzing your personal information in order for us to ensure that we meet your needs. Whenever you use our Internet Services contact us, or use one of the services or facilities offered by Truth Junction pty Ltd, we will collect any information which we have about you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>How we use your Personal Information</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nIn order to ensure that we always meet your needs, we will use your personal information in such ways that we think might assist or benefit you. We may therefore combine all the information that we have about you to compile a profile of you in order for us to personalize and modify our services to your special needs.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nWe will also use your personal information in the ordinary course of our business.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nWe will always ask for your permission before we use your personal information for any purpose not disclosed above.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nAs stated your privacy is important to us.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nWe will not sell, rent or provide your personal information to unauthorized entities or to third parties for their independent use without your consent.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nWe don''t want you to miss out on any of the great deals or promotions we may, or any of our affiliates or business parties or any third party may have from time to time. Thus we may send you promotional material or details by email or by post in order to update you and keep you fully advised of any news, competitions or developments which we think may be of interest to you. If any of this information relates to products, promotions, news or services of any of our affiliates or business parties or a third party, and provided that you indicate that you would like more details and provided that you consent to our disclosure of your contact address to such affiliate, business partner or third party, we may inform the affiliate business partner or third party to contact you directly. You can inform us if you change your mind.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nShould we pass your personal information on to others we will make them aware of the provisions of this privacy policy.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nWe will always strive to make everything we do lawful and legitimate. Therefore, we will release your personal information to a party if we believe that we are required by law or by order of court to do so. We will also disclose your personal information if we believe that it is necessary to prevent or lessen any unlawful or harmful actions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Protection of Personal Information</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nWhen you use the services or facilities provided by Truth Junction pty Ltd, you may be given an user name and password. You must always keep your Internet user name and password secret and ensure that you do not disclose it to anyone.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nWe value the information which you choose to provide us and will therefore take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from loss, misuse or unauthorized alteration.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Correction of Personal Information</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nIf you ever want to update or correct any of your personal information held by us, kindly contact us at www.truthjunction.co.bw</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Personal Information held by or disclosed by you to 3rd parties</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nIf you disclose any personal information directly to any other person or third party, including one of our affiliates or business partners, you must be aware that we do not regulate or control how that person or third party uses your personal information. You should always ensure that you read the privacy policy of any third party.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nWe are not responsible for any representations or information or warranties or content on any web site of any third party. We do not exercise control over third parties'' privacy policies and you should refer to the privacy policy of any third party to see how such party protects your privacy.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Cookies</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nIn your use of our Internet Services, our website uses cookies. In case you were wondering, the word &quot;cookie&quot; refers to information that is sent from the website to your hard drive, where it is saved. In this way, the next time you use the website or any of our Internet Services, we will know who you are and that you have visited the website and used our Internet Services before.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Changes to this Privacy Policy</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nWe may change this privacy policy at any time. Any change to this privacy policy will be displayed on our Web site. If you use this Web site or any of the services or facilities offered by Truth Junction pty Ltd after we have displayed a change to this privacy policy, you will be deemed to have agreed to the change.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Which laws apply</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nThis privacy policy will be governed by the laws of Botswana. You consent to the jurisdiction of the Botswana courts for any dispute which may arise out of this privacy policy.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Refund policy</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nOur refund policy is simple<br />\r\n100 percent satisfaction or 100 percent money back.<br />\r\nPlease feel free to contact us personally in regards to your individual situation should you wish to discuss refunds in more detail.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Delivery policy</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>1.Delivery Notifications</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nyou will receive an email at the address you have specified every time we put a new post on our website. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>2.Delivery timescales</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nOur services will be posted on our website daily and you can access them there.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3.We do not deliver to PO Box numbers.</p>', NULL, '', '2011-08-06', NULL, NULL, 'truth-junction-content.php', '', '');

